    "title": "About Me",
    "bio": "I am a PhD Researcher at the University of L'Aquila (Italy), working at the intersection of Audio Signal Processing, Deep Learning, and the Internet of Sounds. My research focuses on efficient neural network architectures for real-time computational auditory scene analysis and sound event detection.",
